Angelo J. ANELLO, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
SUNCOAST CREDIT UNION, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3056 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 08, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' stipulation for dismissal filed November 7, 2018, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
